E2T3AUD.original: ~z~They might be able to catch this thing on foot. Drive!
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~再不快点他们跑着都能追上了。快开！

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You ever swung one of those things before? For Christ's sake!
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你有没有打过球啊？我的天啊。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I don't pay for 'as soon as I could'.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~拿「尽快」当借口可是没饭吃的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~This is way over your head, dickwad. The head of the LTA is with the Messinas. You can't do nothing.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~这可是上面的大官了，傻逼。交管局的局长支持Messina家族。你拿他没办法。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~you plot, together we get out of it.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你出头脑，就能一起挺过来了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, I came as soon as I could.
~z~you get us out of it. I fight,
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你也带着咱们翻身了。我出肌肉，

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~What's wrong with you, man? You're acting like an asshole.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你咋回事，哥们？对我这么冲干嘛。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~This comes from right up top. The head of the LTA! He's in with the Messinas so you can't do shit.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~这位更是重量级，交管局的局长！他跟Messina家族一伙的，你别想了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I don't know if it's that idiot Evan, or the economy,
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我不知道是因为那个傻逼Evan，还是经济不好，

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Kill the Mex and the Homo if you gotta kill someone.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~非得杀人就杀那个老墨和基佬。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~These fucking guys, stuck in the 1970s or something.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~工会的狗东西，以为自己还活在七十年代是吧。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, you saved me, man, made me.
~z~We're keeping our most important investor happy. Just hit it already.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~咱们要想方设法哄好大金主。你开球就是了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You fucking assholes. The head of the LTA is with the Messinas. There's no way you're gonna get those contracts.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~妈了个逼的，交管局的局长是Messina家族的人。那些合同你拿不到的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Much as it pains me, we better get down there.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~虽然不太乐意，但咱们最好先下去。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I need you to help me get some information out of this union prick who's decided to get an over inflated opinion of himself.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我要你帮我从这个自以为是的工会傻逼嘴里问点话。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~We might just make it. Go. Go.
~z~So, I'll go tell them they gave you the money as a present,
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我去跟他们说，「付的钱是不会还的」。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Gay Tony will always be the king of this town.
~z~You ain't killing us for this shit.
~z~Sleeping with half the women in Liberty City, no doubt.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~全自由城一半的姑娘都被你睡了吧。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~and right now, you and me have to go play nice with one of them
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~现在，你我要去对这帮人笑脸相迎，

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I don't know if I should go out, Lou.
~z~There's a guy works at Libel, the foreman on the Columbus Avenue job. He's the guy holding this up.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~有个LibEl电力的人，他是Columbus大道那个工地的工头。就是他在作对。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Mayors, rivals, drugs, everyone. And this time, I've fucked up.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~当官的、对家的、贩毒的，无敌手。但这一次，我完蛋了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I don't want to die in a golf cart.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我可不想死在高尔夫球车上。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You think I like being like this?
~z~This is just some innocent golf shit.
~z~I guess we got to go help Rocco.
~z~You think that means shit to me? Fuck you.
~z~That's it. Let me fucking go already.
~z~Alright, alright. The other family's got Libel in their pocket. The foreman on the Columbus site's their boy.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我说，我说。LibEl电力已经被别的家族控制了。Columbus大道工地的工头是他们的人。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I work Algonquin nightlife twenty years. I beat everyone.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我在Algonquin的夜店界驰骋二十年，打遍全城无敌手。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Right here. Right now. Needs must, Tone. To be honest, I never fancied the game.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~就在这，现学的。被逼的，Tone。说真的，我从来就不想打高尔夫。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Come on. Put some distance behind us.
~z~Let's just head back to the apartment.
~z~and they each think they own the lot.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~现在他们都觉得两家店是自己的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I find the clothes you have to wear kind of unflattering.
~z~Bend the knees. It's all in the knees.
~z~It's going to be very crowded in the VIP room.
~z~There's got to be someone higher up. Give 'em to me!
~z~How are we meant to outrun them in this thing?
~z~Don't pussy out now, Luis. Hit it.
~z~with the hottest gay and straight clubs at the same time
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~同时拥有最火爆的男同夜店和正常夜店的人。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~These are not nice people and there's a lot of them,
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~他们都不是善茬，还人多势众。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You've met the guy, haven't you? I can't imagine he's got too many friends.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你又不是没见过他，他像是有很多朋友吗？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~What's wrong with you slick haired Momma's boys?
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你们这帮油腻妈宝男都有病吧？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Alright. Okay. Mel Toblowsky with Libel says he ain't gonna comply. He's working down Columbus Avenue.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~好，我说。LibEl电力的Mel Toblowsky说他不可能同意。他在Columbus大道的工地。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~They know where I am, assholes. I wouldn't wanna be you.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~他们知道我在哪，傻逼。你们等死吧。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Head down to the pier. We're meeting Rock at the driving range.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~去码头。我们去旁边的高尔夫球场见Rock。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~That ain't it. You and me know, that ain't it!
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~不止吧。大家都知道，不止两个！

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You don't wanna be fucking with me.
~z~You guys are fucked, okay? The Messinas are gonna be all over your ass.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你们完了，知道吗？Messina家族的人会来追杀你们的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Tony, shit, you got burrito breath. You ain't been eating Mexican again have you?
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~Tony，你他妈一股卷饼味，是不是又吃墨西哥菜了？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~When things calm down me and you should hit the links in Venturas.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~等这事完了，咱们去拉斯文加斯练练高尔夫。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Who ain't playing ball then? Give it up.
~z~Yo Rock, you've invested in the wrong clubs, man. Maybe Split Sides is more your vibe.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~哟，Rock，你这夜店买错了，哥们。喜剧俱乐部更适合你。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~How am I supposed to hit it with you in my ear?
~z~Sure thing, Tone. I can just see us now, a pair of terrible golfers, who just lost another million playing craps.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~好啊，Tone。有画面了，两个高尔夫菜鸡，为了打这破球又花了几百万。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I don't want to think about the trouble we'll be in if they kill Rocco. Let's get down there.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~要是Rocco死了，我们可就麻烦大了。快下去吧。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You and I both know that ain't it.
~z~I take them to the special VIP room at the bottom of the West River.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我就把他们送到西河河底的雅座。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~- Yeah yeah you fuck, you missed me bitch. ~n~- I'm gonna get down there and go talk to him.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~－是啊，是啊，操你妈的，你他妈打不中我。~n~－我要下去跟他好好聊聊。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~and I am about to lose everything.
~z~We're meeting Rocco at the driving range.
~z~I'll handle these guys. Keep in cover.
~z~That's it. Go. Go. Go. We might be in the clear.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~就是这样，冲冲冲！我们会没事的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Oh, baa da boom. I'm sure I woulda found that funny if I spoke spic.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~噢，这人真是。我懂西语的话应该就能找到笑点了吧。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~That was a pleasant outing, Rock. Where's that put us with you know what? We square?
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~玩得真开心啊，Rock。这次惹的麻烦也太大了吧？扯平了没？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~There's got to be more than just those two!
~z~You Dominicans is meant to be athletes.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~不是说多米尼加人天生就是运动员吗。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Real shame, I'll have to ask my maid to translate for me.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~可惜我只能叫女佣帮我翻译。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Any moment now my protection's gonna show and you guys are screwed.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我的靠山随时都可能出现，然后你们就完了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~so they don't start sending rent a goombah into the club.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~这样才不至于被他们派人到店里砸场。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Square? What you borrowed? At those points? You ain't even making a dent on the interest.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~扯平？你欠了多少啊？就这么点吗？今天的事还个利息都不够。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Don't Rocco have someone else to hit the batting cage for him?
~z~Ain't you spics meant to have decent swings? Do it.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你们西班牙佬不是很擅长高尔夫吗？来吧。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~-You missed. You swing like a fag.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~这都打不着。挥杆还跟个基佬似的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~That was a pleasant outing, Rock. Where's that put us with you know what? We square?
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~玩得真开心啊，Rock。这次惹的麻烦也太大了吧？扯平了没？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You people is more suited to being caddies. Shit.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你这人更适合当球童，他妈的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Come on. Let's head back to the apartment.
~z~You wanna step up, be my guest.
~z~or this fucking cocaine or the pills, which I am not taking anymore,
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~还是因为傻逼可卡因或是止痛药，虽然我现在也不嗑了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I ain't letting you off that easy.
~z~Square? What you borrowed? At those points?
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~扯平？你欠了多少啊？就这么点吗？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I thought they bred you tacos for sports.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我还以为你们老墨天生就是搞运动的料。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I've done a deal with the wrong devil, man.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~这笔交易要让我万劫不复了，哥们。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Shit! Jack Duffy's their guy with the Transport Workers Union. Okay?
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的！运输工会的Jack Duffy是他们的人。够了吗？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I hope you didn't miss on purpose there.
~z~You got more than that. I know it.
~z~You ain't even making a dent on the interest and muscles over there killed our friend.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~今天的事还个利息都不够，大块头还把那位朋友给杀了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You're not going to win any tour championships, that's for sure.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你这肯定打不了巡回锦标赛，真的。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Gimme the rest of them, you piece of shit.
~z~You fucking missed me you, you piece of shit. Fucking prick.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~你他妈没打中啊，你个废物，你个傻逼。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Besides, I'm about to have to do all the messy work on this guy myself.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~再说了，这家伙的烂摊子还得靠我亲自收拾。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~I hear Jack Duffy with the TWU might be with them. Okay, now fuck off already.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~我听说运输工会的Jack Duffy跟他们是一伙的。好了，快放我走吧。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Oh, where the fuck have you been, man?
~z~You gonna tell me who's holding out?
~z~I sold the business to two different people
~z~Where'd you learn to play golf, Lou?
~z~Hey yo, I didn't kill him, I might be about to kill you in a second though.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，他不是我杀的，不过我现在想杀你了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~In case you were wondering, I'm not enjoying this any more.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~不知道你想不想知道，我一点都不想这样。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~No! But I-I-I told you shit. I told you everything.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~不！我、我不都招了吗。我什么都说了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~You hit him with some balls when I tell you to. You think you can that do for me, Louise?
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~等我发话了，你就给他来几球。有没有信心，Louise？

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~There they are. The spic and the fag.
~z~Alright, okay, okay, Jack Duffy, with the Transport Workers. He's getting fat off the other guys.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~好，我说，我说。Jack Duffy，还有运输工会的人。他收了别人的好处。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Fuck you, alright? Fuck you, there ain't nothing else.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~操你妈，听到了吗？操你妈，我全都招了。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~Sure. But we've never been this fucked before.
~z~Keep your dog on a leash, Tony. See you ladies later.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~让你的狗腿子老实点，Tony。两位姑娘再见。

E2T3AUD.original: ~z~We only got one behind us now. Thank Moses.
E2T3AUD.translated: ~z~现在就剩最后一辆了。谢天谢地。
